==English==

===Etymology===
From the name of the Thaypan tribe of [[Aboriginal]] people of central [[Cape York Peninsula]], [[Queensland]], [[Australia]].

===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
{{en-noun-reg}}
# any of a [[venomous]] species of [[snake]], of the family ''[[Elapidae]]'', found in [[Australia]] and [[New Guinea]]
# a [[foreign]] [[businessman]] in [[China]]; a [[tycoon]]
